of moving in nature?

00:05:20.340 --> 00:05:25.200 align:middle line:10%
In 1966, Marian Diamond
took two groups of mice.

00:05:25.200 --> 00:05:27.900 align:middle line:10%
One she put in a very
enriched environment

00:05:27.900 --> 00:05:31.710 align:middle line:10%
