levels, and unique spaces

00:05:31.710 --> 00:05:33.390 align:middle line:10%
to play around in.

00:05:33.390 --> 00:05:36.600 align:middle line:84%
The other group was set
in simply an open box.

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:40.560 align:middle line:84%
Nothing to play with, no
toys, no unique spaces.

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:43.770 align:middle line:84%
She found that those mice
in the enriched environment

00:05:43.770 --> 00:05:46.140 align:middle line:84%
had increased glial
cell activation.

00:05:46.140 --> 00:05:50.140 align:middle line:84%
That basically means new
brain cells being generated.

00:05:50.140 --> 00:05:53.670 align:middle line:84%
They also showed better
cognitive performance simply

00:05:53.670 --> 00:05:57.120 align:middle line:84%
from being in a more
enriched environment.

00:05:57.120 --> 00:06:02.410 align:middle line:84%
