learn many of their motor,

00:06:05.910 --> 00:06:08.970 align:middle line:84%
social, and even
self-confidence building skills

00:06:08.970 --> 00:06:10.680 align:middle line:90%
through the act of play.

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:14.370 align:middle line:84%
There are even studies showing
that child development thrives

00:06:14.370 --> 00:06:15.690 align:middle line:90%
on play.

00:06:15.690 --> 00:06:18.840 align:middle line:10%
This article concludes
play and guided

00:06:18.840 --> 00:06:23.320 align:middle line:10%
