00:18:46.190 --> 00:18:47.640 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:18:47.640 --> 00:18:51.330 align:middle line:84%
Because introducing play
into our moments of service

00:18:51.330 --> 00:18:56.280 align:middle line:84%
